title: File:Incheon Newcomers tour (8801828).jpg
author: U.S. Army photo by Spc. Philemon Tan
description: U.S. Soldiers with the 55th Military Police Company pose for photo at The Inspire Entertainment Resort, Incheon, South Korea, Dec. 12. The Inspire Entertainment Resort is one of many attractions in the Incheon area and provides soldiers an outlook on what the country of South Korea has to offer. (U.S. Army photo by Spc Philemon Tan)
